      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's definitely a bit intense, but i've had bad indigestion before and it feels pretty much the same. i don't really want to go to the ER if i don't have to, it's such a hassle. you think it’s probably just the pizza and i'm overthinking the arm thing? like, can i just take a couple extra antacids and see if it goes away in like an hour?",
